---
title: Rigatoni and Beef Rosé Marinara with Roasted Pepper Pesto and Spinach
description: This creamy rosé sauce is a game changer for your weeknight meals. Our easy cheat version uses cream cheese to add richness without making the dish too heavy. The delicious beef flavour shines through!
